you know, like I said, I have a great team. We're almost always saying yes. Like, can you also look

00:55:20.239 --> 00:55:24.000
at this? Yep, we'll do it, right? Sometimes maybe it's like, I don't really think that's going to

00:55:24.000 --> 00:55:28.399
matter, but honestly it doesn't matter. They think it matters, so let's go find out. And so a lot of

00:55:28.399 --> 00:55:32.000
it is just sometimes just sort of saying, yep, yep, we're going to look at every possible angle

00:55:32.000 --> 00:55:38.719
and try a bunch of different things. Okay, I know that this hour is always the fastest hour for

