you're in a team with, a league with 10 players, you probably didn't improve your chances much more

00:56:01.199 --> 00:56:05.840
from like 10% to 20%. I've lost plenty. We also have very strict restrictions about what we can

00:56:05.840 --> 00:56:10.479
and can't play, so I'm going to just note that I used to play it a lot more than I'm allowed to now.

